        "title": "Introducing Pixate Studio beta",
        "comment": "Hey DN! Today we're launching a private beta of Pixate Studio. Pixate Studio is a completely standalone version of Pixate that runs on your desktop, allowing you to work from anywhere (even on a plane!) and store your prototypes locally. Join the beta here (you don't need a Pixate account):\r\n\r\nhttp://www.pixate.com/studio/\r\n\r\nWe're also working on features to allow you to import and export prototypes between Pixate and Pixate Studio, so you'll be able to seamlessly use Pixate anywhere. \r\n\r\nWe hope you guys are as excited about this as we are!",
